# Local planning notes, not part of the deployed state.
reference/**

# Secret key material — MUST never be committed. The age private key lives in
# ~/.config/sops/age/keys.txt on the admin workstation and in-cluster as the
# `sops-age` secret. Encrypted `*.sops.yaml` files ARE committed (safe); these
# patterns guard against accidentally adding a raw key or an unencrypted dump.
*.agekey
keys.txt
age-key*.txt

# Local kubeconfig copies, if ever placed in-repo by mistake.
kubeconfig
*.kubeconfig
